256
00:14:19,859 --> 00:14:21,319
Ang kasariwaan ang lahat.

257
00:14:21,402 --> 00:14:22,904
Sinusubukan mong panatilihing sariwa ang mga ito

258
00:14:22,987 --> 00:14:24,739
