306
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:40,541
Kumander ng Batalyon!

307
00:16:40,625 --> 00:16:42,418
Dahil ba ito sa sopas ng damong-dagat, ginoo?

308
00:16:43,377 --> 00:16:45,588
Naayos na iyan ng Battalion Commander .

309
00:16:45,671 --> 00:16:46,839
Bakit ko naman ba ito babanggitin?

310
00:16:46,923 --> 00:16:48,591
Nag-aalala lang ako sa'yo.

311
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:51,844
Nauuna kang gumising at nauubusan kang aalis,
at wala ka ngang pahinga tuwing Sabado at Linggo.

312
00:16:51,928 --> 00:16:53,554
Naisip ko na baka masyadong malupit

313
00:16:53,638 --> 00:16:56,057
