314
00:16:59,727 --> 00:17:00,728
Ayos lang ako, ginoo.

315
00:17:00,811 --> 00:17:02,939
- At nasisiyahan akong matuto ng mga bagong bagay.
- Sige.

316
00:17:03,314 --> 00:17:04,315
Sige.

317
00:17:06,817 --> 00:17:08,736
Alam ko nang eksakto ang ibig mong sabihin.

318
00:17:10,238 --> 00:17:12,073
Kahit sinusubukan kong maging madaling lapitan

319
00:17:12,448 --> 00:17:14,492
Hindi siguro naging madali para sa iyo
ang magbukas ng isip at magsalita nang tapat.

320
00:17:14,742 --> 00:17:15,743
May tendensiya akong maging...

321
