356
00:19:31,879 --> 00:19:33,381
Hindi ako susuko.

357
00:19:35,049 --> 00:19:36,217
Kasama ko kayo ni Mama.

358
00:19:36,926 --> 00:19:37,968
Kailangan kong malampasan ito.

359
00:19:45,518 --> 00:19:46,519
Ang tatay ko

360
